<item>
            <title>[LU-7714] osd_objset_open() misuses GOTO()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7714</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In &lt;tt&gt;osd_objset_open()&lt;/tt&gt; we fail to propagate errors by using &lt;tt&gt;GOTO(out, -ENOTSUPP)&lt;/tt&gt; instead of &lt;tt&gt;GOTO(out, rc = -ENOTSUPP)&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
